Dependency:

    gcc
    make
    cmake
    automoc4

Install:

  sudo ./install.sh

Postinstall (needed just because some icon are not loaded by plasma after installing the software):

    Reboot or give:

    kquitapp plasma-desktop
    plasma-desktop

Uninstall:
  
  Disable configuration lines in time.conf access.conf:

    sudo ./uninstall.sh

  Purge configuration lines in time.conf access.conf

    sudo ./uninstall.sh purge

Note:
  
  If you remove the build directory you will not be able to uninstall the software. In this case reinstall it and then remove it with the scripts.